<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="408" type="distribution">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6870952" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6870952" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6870952/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="408" targetBox="[1439,2031,1098,1513]" targetPageId="15">
<paragraph blockId="15.[2054,2648,1098,1517]" pageId="15" pageNumber="408">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[2054,2226,1365,1398]" pageId="15" pageNumber="408">Distribution.</emphasis>
Known only from Reserva Ecologica Huitepec, C Chiapas, SE Mexico.
</paragraph>
</caption>
