<subSubSection pageId="15" pageNumber="408" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="15.[1439,2646,1522,2185]" pageId="15" pageNumber="408">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1441,1787,1956,1989]" pageId="15" pageNumber="408">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Critically Endangered on The IUCN Red List. The Pale-toothed Shrew is found only in one location in a protected area (Reserva Ecologica Huitepec), its known extent of occurrence is less than 100 km? and it seems to be threatened by habitat loss from agricultural expansion and general deforestation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
